10. App Screens Summary
------------------------

  AUTH FLOW (5 screens):
    Splash → Onboarding → Sign Up → Verify OTP → Success

  MAIN APP (10 screens):
    Home Dashboard          — Search, fuel filters, station cards, AI promo banner
    Nearby Stations         — All stations with filter chips (All/Open/Short Queue/Nearest)
    Station Details         — Hero image, fuel grid, queue card, prediction, action buttons
    Report Queue            — Queue level + fuel checkboxes + vehicle count selector
    Live Queue Tracking     — Simulated map with route, ETA, and station info sheet
    AI Predictions          — Best time card, busy hour chart, trend analysis
    Profile                 — User card, menu options, sign out
    Saved Addresses         — Home/Work/Other locations list
    Notifications           — Alert feed with icons and timestamps
    Success (reusable)      — Configurable confirmation screen
